Package: metricsd
Version: cedfe36
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Your Name <your.email@example.com>
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.31), systemd
Recommends: ca-certificates
Description: System and application metrics collector
 metricsd is a lightweight metrics collector with plugin support.
 It can collect system metrics (CPU, memory, disk, network, GPU)
 and ship them to various backends (Prometheus, Splunk HEC, HTTP JSON).
 .
 Features:
  - Built-in system metrics collectors
  - Plugin system for extensibility
  - Multiple shipper backends
  - Systemd integration
  - TLS support
